  "title": "Senior Staff Nurse (JR1102)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>The Opportunity:</strong></u></p>\n<p>We are looking for Senior /Staff Nurse to join us for various disciplines to provide high quality patient care.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<p>The incumbent shall be responsible to:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assess, plan, implement and evaluate care for patients in the appropriate discipline under the direction of the Nurse Clinician in the individual units</li>\n  <li>Provide high quality patient care in various disciplines by performing clinical procedures that will meet the patients’ immediate physical and emotional needs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Nursing or State Registered Nurse Certificate</li>\n  <li>Relevant Advanced Nursing Diploma or equivalent is preferred for candidate applying or the Senior Staff Nurse position</li>\n</ul>",
